OL,3,CPlans for the 'most high-tech,
OL,4,Cdigitally advanced hospital in the UK'
OL,6,FThe rebuild of a hospital in Leighton
OL,7,FHospital in Crewe is up for discussion
OL,8,Fand local residents are being
OL,9,Fencouraged to have their say.
OL,11,FThe hospital opened in the 1970s and
OL,12,Fplans for a new building were
OL,13,Fconfirmed two years ago.
OL,15,FIt promises to be "the UK's most
OL,16,Fdigitally-advanced" facility when it
OL,17,Fopens in around five years time.
