OL,3,CPlans for the 'most high-tech,
OL,4,Cdigitally advanced hospital in the UK'
OL,6,FMid Cheshire Hospitals NHS Foundation
OL,7,FTrust launched the four-week public
OL,8,Fconsultation with a host of
OL,9,Finformation events:
OL,11,FThe outline planning application for
OL,12,Fthe new hospital will be submitted to
OL,13,FCheshire East Council in December. It
OL,14,Fincudes:
OL,16,FRuss Favager, the Trust's Board Senior
OL,17,FResponsible Officer for Leighton New
OL,18,FHospital Programme, said:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
