OL,3,CPlans for the 'most high-tech,
OL,4,Cdigitally advanced hospital in the UK'
OL,6,F"This is an exciting time, as we have
OL,7,Fa once in a generation opportunity to
OL,8,Fchange how healthcare is delivered. I
OL,9,Fwould strongly encourage people to
OL,10,Fattend the events and be part of this
OL,11,Fshared journey.
OL,13,F"We have a bold ambition to create a
OL,14,Fhealth and care neighbourhood with a
OL,15,Fnew Leighton at its heart. The new
OL,16,Fhospital is being designed so meet the
OL,17,Fneeds of a growing population, while
OL,18,Fimproving how patients access them,
OL,19,Fensuring the right care, at the right
OL,20,Ftime, in the right place."
