OL,4,Cdigitally advanced hospital in the UK'
OL,6,FThe proposed new Leighton hospital
OL,7,Fwill be one of the most high-tech,
OL,8,Fdigitally advanced hospitals in the
OL,9,FUK. It will be built on the land
OL,10,Fpurchased in 2024 to the north of the
OL,11,Fexisting hospital site in Crewe.
